        "similarity",
        "dissimilarity"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "首先，我们需要两个概念：",
        "<term id=\"similarity\">相似性</term> 越高，对象越像，通常在0到1之间。",
        "<term id=\"dissimilarity\">相异性</term>（或距离）越高，对象差异越大。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "euclidean_distance",
        "manhattan_distance",
        "minkowski_distance"
      ],
      "id": "s046",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "euclidean_distance",
        "manhattan_distance",
        "minkowski_distance"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "对于数值数据（场景3），常用距离：",
        "<term id=\"euclidean_distance\">欧氏距离</term>：直线距离，\\(\\sqrt{\\sum (p_k - q_k)^2}\\)",
        "<term id=\"manhattan_distance\">曼哈顿距离</term>：网格距离，\\(\\sum |p_k - q_k|\\)",
        "它们都是 <term id=\"minkowski_distance\">闵可夫斯基距离</term> 的特例（r=2 欧氏，r=1 曼哈顿）。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "cosine_similarity"
      ],
      "id": "s047",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "cosine_similarity"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "对于文档数据（场景2），常用 <term id=\"cosine_similarity\">余弦相似度</term>。",
        "它关注两个向量的方向是否一致，而不是长度。",
        "因为文档长度差异大，但内容可能相似。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "jaccard_coefficient"
      ],
      "id": "s048",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "jaccard_coefficient"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "对于非对称二元数据（场景1），常用 <term id=\"jaccard_coefficient\">Jaccard 系数</term>。",
        "它只考虑双方都为1的情况，忽略双方都为0的情况。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
